List Available CWB Corpora.

Source: R/cqp.R
cqp_list_corpora.Rd

List the corpora described by the registry files in the registry directory that is currently set.

cqp_list_corpora()

Author

Andreas Blaette, Bernard Desgraupes, Sylvain Loiseau
